1
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,870
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,340 --> 00:01:37,770
[Episode 1]

3
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,840
Extra! Extra!

4
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:13,840
Murong Qingyi, the outcast of 2 families,
has been released from prison!

5
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,590
Extra! Extra!

6
00:02:15,590 --> 00:02:19,650
Murong Qingyi, the outcast of 2 families,
has been released from prison!

7
00:02:19,710 --> 00:02:21,030
He's marrying into the Huo family,

8
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:22,840
climbing the ladder by landing Miss Huo,

9
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:25,310
and selling himself for a good price!

10
00:02:32,950 --> 00:02:35,810
[Grand Theatre]

11
00:02:38,650 --> 00:02:39,750
[Opening]

12
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:41,860
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

13
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:42,720
[Officially Open]

14
00:02:44,750 --> 00:02:45,480
You're here.

15
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,960
Our big star is
getting more and more popular.

16
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:48,680
Mr. Huo.

17
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,610
Not even an "I missed you"?

18
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:54,280
Come find me after this.

19
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:57,070
[Huo Zongqi, Heir to the Huo Family]

20
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:57,960
Mr. Li!

21
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:01,870
Good to see you.

22
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,620
Don't pull a long face.

23
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:08,960
It's a big day.

24
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,910
Don't let our in-laws, the Murongs,
look down on us.

25
00:03:09,770 --> 00:03:13,380
[Huo Minxian,
From a Branch of the Huo Family]

26
00:03:11,910 --> 00:03:12,360
In-laws?

27
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,220
Please come in.

28
00:03:13,710 --> 00:03:15,560
You forced me into marrying

29
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,960
that good-for-nothing
from the Murong family,

30
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:21,020
yet here you are,
so quick to call each other "in-laws."

31
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:24,380
You're no treasured daughter
of the family either.

32
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:26,150
I think it's a good match.

33
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:33,450
[Yang Yuelian, Huo Minxian's Mother]

34
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:37,130
You too, don't pull a long face.

35
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,190
Cheng Army passing through!

36
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,790
All civilians, stand clear!

37
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,710
Make way, make way!

38
00:03:51,710 --> 00:03:52,750
-Out of the way!
-Stop staring!

39
00:03:52,750 --> 00:03:53,480
Stand aside!

40
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,360
Out of the way!

41
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:39,620
[Cheng Jinzhi, Madam Murong]

42
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:50,159
[Murong Qingyu, Eldest Son of the Murong Family;
Principal of Zhenhua Aviation School]

43
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:51,870
Madam Murong.

44
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:52,800
Qingyu.

45
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,010
Congratulations.

46
00:04:55,430 --> 00:04:57,960
Your family's business is
growing stronger.

47
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,270
You flatter me, Madam Murong.

48
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,730
It's only a movie theater,

49
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,920
for entertainment, nothing more.

50
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:04,630
In the future,

51
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:06,070
we'll still be relying on your support,

52
00:05:06,070 --> 00:05:07,600
and yours as well, Qingyu.

53
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,080
By the way,

54
00:05:11,630 --> 00:05:13,290
where is Young Master Qingyi?

55
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,720
It's a marriage
between the younger generation.

56
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,000
We elders have made

57
00:05:17,000 --> 00:05:18,730
our decision, and that's that.

58
00:05:18,830 --> 00:05:21,090
There's no need for him to come in person.

59
00:05:21,920 --> 00:05:23,920
Minxian and your second son are engaged,

60
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:25,250
but they have never met.

61
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,320
-Isn't it...
-Today,

62
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,800
we're here to celebrate
your family's new venture.

63
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,830
As for Qingyi,

64
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:31,920
we can discuss that matter later.

65
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,980
There is nothing further to discuss.

66
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:52,320
Don't worry, Qingyu.

67
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,190
Now that we're in-laws,

68
00:05:54,510 --> 00:05:56,710
the Huo family will treat you as our own.

69
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,800
When it comes to
military supplies and equipment,

70
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:00,730
we will certainly prioritize you.

71
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,270
Besides, now that you're
in charge of the aviation school,

72
00:06:05,270 --> 00:06:06,190
we

73
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,870
will definitely give you our full support.

74
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,830
I was appointed by my superiors
to head the aviation school.

75
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,830
It doesn't belong to me personally.

76
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,560
If you truly wish to
help the aviation school for the sake

77
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,310
of the country and its people,

78
00:06:16,310 --> 00:06:17,950
then I thank you on its behalf.

79
00:06:17,950 --> 00:06:19,430
But if it's for the sake of
this marriage alliance,

80
00:06:19,430 --> 00:06:20,160
then...

81
00:06:21,070 --> 00:06:22,190
there's no need.

82
00:06:39,380 --> 00:06:41,470
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

83
00:06:42,130 --> 00:06:43,240
Did they come together?

84
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:44,409
I think so.

85
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:00,720
Isn't that Murong Qingyi,
the Second Young Master

86
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,720
of the Murong family?

87
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,120
Wasn't he in prison?

88
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,280
I heard he was just released.

89
00:07:05,430 --> 00:07:07,160
I heard that Second Young Master Murong

90
00:07:07,160 --> 00:07:08,430
still has the blood of a Huo on his hands.

91
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:09,390
[Murong Qingyi,
Second Son of the Murong Family]

92
00:07:08,870 --> 00:07:09,510
And yet,

93
00:07:09,510 --> 00:07:12,440
the two families
can still form a marriage alliance?

94
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,390
Absurd.

95
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,750
Do you really think you're worthy

96
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:33,810
of wearing the Cheng Army's uniform?

97
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,830
Father once commanded the Cheng Army.

98
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:37,870
Wearing this uniform

99
00:07:37,870 --> 00:07:38,720
is simply my way

100
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,360
of honoring him.

101
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,430
Mother, haven't you worn

102
00:07:42,430 --> 00:07:44,920
-that uniform your entire life as well...
-You have no right to speak of him.

103
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,120
Take the uniform off.

104
00:07:52,950 --> 00:07:53,630
Mother,

105
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,390
Qingyi has his family on his mind.

106
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:56,310
That's a good thing.

107
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:58,040
You're always taking his side.

108
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,270
Brother, if you really want
what's best for me,

109
00:08:00,270 --> 00:08:02,680
why don't you marry the Huo girl yourself?

110
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:10,800
We'll talk about your marriage
when we get back.

111
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,460
Don't embarrass Mother here.

112
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,410
You just got out of prison,

113
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,140
so naturally, you don't know.

114
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,300
Your elder brother

115
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,270
has long been engaged to the only daughter

116
00:08:21,270 --> 00:08:23,130
of the Nanyang shipping magnate.

117
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,680
So that's how it is.

118
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,890
No wonder you suddenly thought of me.

119
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:28,720
And here I thought

120
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,520
you'd long forgotten I existed.

121
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,360
Minxian

122
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:37,150
may be from a collateral branch
of our family,

123
00:08:37,150 --> 00:08:39,909
but this marriage is meant to
strengthen our alliance.

124
00:08:39,909 --> 00:08:42,240
She's a perfectly suitable match for you,

125
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:43,710
Young Master Qingyi.

126
00:08:49,670 --> 00:08:52,030
Since the marriage is
about strengthening ties,

127
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:53,360
Young Master Huo, why don't you

128
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,600
move straight into the Cheng Army barracks

129
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:57,120
and grow old alongside the soldiers?

130
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,650
Wouldn't that be
much more straightforward?

131
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,510
Insolent.

132
00:09:04,550 --> 00:09:06,440
I grew up without parental discipline,

133
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,910
so I'm used to speaking without restraint.

134
00:09:07,910 --> 00:09:09,840
Please be understanding, Mother!

135
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,260
Speaking of, Mrs. Huo.

136
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:14,910
No,

137
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:16,720
Mother-in-law.

138
00:09:17,720 --> 00:09:19,000
Is Minxian feeling shy?

139
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:19,730
Where is she?

140
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:25,030
You haven't had your wedding yet.

141
00:09:25,030 --> 00:09:27,000
There is no need for you
to change how you address me.

142
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,930
I'll go in first.

143
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,600
There's no need

144
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,640
to embarrass Mother in front of outsiders.

145
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:55,000
I was sold for a good price by you all.

146
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:57,520
Who's the one being embarrassed here?

147
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:11,910
[Mingguang Grand Theater]

148
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,720
Why don't you just drop dead?

149
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:21,810
Are you making a wish, Miss Huo?

150
00:10:22,870 --> 00:10:24,330
If you want to make wishes,

151
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,140
a temple is the place for that.

152
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:29,510
I will never marry
the murderer of my father.

153
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,750
What a pity.

154
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,200
Neither of us

155
00:10:34,390 --> 00:10:35,990
has any say in this marriage.

156
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:41,030
You're just a piece of trash
the Li family ruined,

157
00:10:41,390 --> 00:10:44,240
the murderer of my father.

158
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,390
Why are you still alive?

159
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,320
Why?

160
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,030
Perhaps

161
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,790
because I'm a Murong.

162
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:02,080
And yet here you are,
shamelessly calling yourself a Murong?

163
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:04,210
Does the Murong family even claim you?

164
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:09,510
Miss Huo,

165
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:12,670
we're both just pawns
in our families' interests.

166
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:14,330
Don't get too lost in the role.

167
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:17,670
Murong Qingyi,

168
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:20,200
I will definitely make

169
00:11:20,390 --> 00:11:21,150
your life

170
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:22,270
a

171
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,080
living

172
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,390
hell.

173
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,030
Good.

174
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:31,790
I'll be waiting.

175
00:11:40,490 --> 00:11:41,450
What's going on?

176
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:42,640
What are you doing?

177
00:11:42,670 --> 00:11:43,690
Is that Huo Minxian?

178
00:11:43,690 --> 00:11:44,450
It's her.

179
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:46,600
I think she's seducing Murong Qingyi.

180
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,270
What are they doing?

181
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:52,240
The man in the car is not

182
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:54,570
the second young master of Murong, right?

183
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:55,680
What's going on?

184
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:56,550
Stop the screening!

185
00:11:56,550 --> 00:11:57,880
Stop the screening now!

186
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,530
I said, stop the screening!

187
00:11:59,530 --> 00:11:59,750
Hurry!

188
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:00,990
This is so embarrassing.

189
00:12:00,990 --> 00:12:01,770
Hurry up, hurry.

190
00:12:01,770 --> 00:12:02,810
Film this.

191
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,200
Stop taking pictures!

192
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,240
What's with this?

193
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,150
Stop filming it!

194
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:07,270
Get someone to stop the screening!

195
00:12:07,270 --> 00:12:08,400
Stop the screening!

196
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:10,870
-Stop taking pictures! All of you!
-Find someone to stop it!

197
00:12:10,870 --> 00:12:11,790
Stop it!

198
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:14,200
Stop the screening! I said, stop it!

199
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,580
Stop taking pictures! All of you!

200
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:21,740
Stop taking pictures!

201
00:12:22,030 --> 00:12:24,160
Stop it! Which newspaper are you from?

202
00:12:24,270 --> 00:12:25,400
Put the camera down!

203
00:12:25,550 --> 00:12:26,630
Murong Qingyi,

204
00:12:26,630 --> 00:12:27,910
you're so despicable!

205
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:36,000
What a good show.

206
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:36,790
You...

207
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:37,270
Stop taking pictures! Stop it!

208
00:12:37,270 --> 00:12:38,600
-You…
-Stop making trouble!

209
00:12:38,600 --> 00:12:38,910
Stop taking pictures.

210
00:12:38,910 --> 00:12:39,720
-Someone!
-Who's causing trouble?

211
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,980
Stop taking pictures!

212
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:41,910
Stop it!

213
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:42,970
Put the camera down!

214
00:12:42,970 --> 00:12:43,550
Put the camera down!

215
00:12:43,550 --> 00:12:44,720
Seize them all!

216
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,550
Put the camera down!

217
00:12:45,550 --> 00:12:46,960
-Put it down!
-Stop taking pictures!

218
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,630
Stop taking pictures!

219
00:12:47,630 --> 00:12:48,760
Stop the screening!

220
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,400
Young Master,

221
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,300
what happened?

222
00:13:10,960 --> 00:13:12,320
Go check the projection room.

223
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:14,050
The footage must not be leaked.

224
00:13:18,630 --> 00:13:20,360
This is the story of the century!

225
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,000
Yeah.

226
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,620
Stop taking pictures!

227
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:30,370
All of you, stop taking pictures!

228
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,390
Murong Qingyi.

229
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:40,960
Quite the surprise you've given us.

230
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,080
You flatter me, Mother.

231
00:13:47,120 --> 00:13:48,630
Absurd and shameless.

232
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:51,080
How could I have a child like you?

233
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:05,480
Young Master Qingyi,

234
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,120
bad news.

235
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:08,760
Someone got to
the film negative before us.

236
00:14:09,670 --> 00:14:10,530
What happened?

237
00:14:10,870 --> 00:14:12,720
The projectionist was knocked out.

238
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:14,450
Only this was left at the scene.

239
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,030
This is...

240
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:20,240
a gentian flower?

241
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:24,250
My family used to
grow many gentian flowers.

242
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,270
It'd be nice if you

243
00:14:26,270 --> 00:14:28,870
had some gentian flowers planted
in your yard.

244
00:14:30,390 --> 00:14:32,250
You teach me how to plant flowers,

245
00:14:32,360 --> 00:14:33,960
and I'll teach you the tango.

246
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:47,600
Susu!

247
00:14:49,670 --> 00:14:50,750
Susu!

248
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,200
Hello,

249
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,080
I'd like to buy some flowers.

250
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:14,870
Susu...

251
00:15:18,290 --> 00:15:21,180
♪ Hate is the smoke left by dying flames ♪

252
00:15:22,300 --> 00:15:24,670
♪ Love is the warmth
lingering after the wildfire ♪

253
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:28,420
♪ Love and hate collide in a blaze ♪

254
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:32,630
♪ In this instant,
the flames rage out of control ♪

255
00:15:30,150 --> 00:15:31,030
Susu!

256
00:15:32,730 --> 00:15:35,420
♪ Ahead lies
a tangle of joys and sorrows ♪

257
00:15:36,900 --> 00:15:38,860
♪ Behind remain
the bitterness of unspoken feelings ♪

258
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:43,160
♪ The heart races with every thought ♪

259
00:15:43,260 --> 00:15:46,370
♪ Yet remains forever bound ♪

260
00:15:46,470 --> 00:15:49,520
♪ Is it a blessing or a curse? ♪

261
00:15:48,630 --> 00:15:49,200
Hello.

262
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,600
Sorry.

263
00:15:53,210 --> 00:15:55,810
♪ If the sparks ♪

264
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,860
I got the wrong person.

265
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:58,380
♪ Could fly back into the gun's muzzle ♪

266
00:16:01,580 --> 00:16:05,670
♪ If I had turned away
when love first bloomed ♪

267
00:16:08,830 --> 00:16:13,990
♪ Perhaps I could've
walked away unscathed ♪

268
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:20,310
♪ Sadly, fate leaves no room for "if" ♪

269
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:23,750
This flower is so beautiful.

270
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:24,520
♪ Lies ♪

271
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:24,600
Thank you.

272
00:16:24,630 --> 00:16:27,870
♪ Know better than my foes ♪

273
00:16:30,040 --> 00:16:31,690
♪ How to settle in ♪

274
00:16:31,800 --> 00:16:34,660
♪ The void within me ♪

275
00:16:37,790 --> 00:16:43,130
♪ My true heart hides in the shadows,
left to fate's mercy ♪

276
00:16:44,700 --> 00:16:50,470
♪ Resisting the pull of every temptation ♪

277
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:47,750
She's already dead.

278
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,750
What am I still hoping for?

279
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:54,110
♪ This spark of wildfire
spreading across the plains ♪

280
00:16:55,040 --> 00:16:57,710
♪ Stirs embers that refuse to fade ♪

281
00:16:58,640 --> 00:17:01,580
♪ I seize fate by the hand ♪

282
00:17:01,660 --> 00:17:05,260
♪ Accusing it of refusing to relent ♪

283
00:17:05,980 --> 00:17:08,650
♪ Pain and joy blur before my eyes ♪

284
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:12,569
♪ Fate keeps replaying its endless cycle ♪

285
00:17:12,619 --> 00:17:18,310
♪ The love that refused to die ♪

286
00:17:19,859 --> 00:17:23,849
♪ Has already consumed us both ♪

287
00:17:25,240 --> 00:17:26,349
Murong Qingyi.

288
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,840
It's been a long time.

289
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:46,720
Bitch!

290
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:49,720
Not only did you
disgrace the Murong family,

291
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,830
but you even trampled all over

292
00:17:50,830 --> 00:17:52,070
the Huo family's reputation.

293
00:17:52,070 --> 00:17:53,200
You got a death wish?

294
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:55,560
You think I fear Murong Qingyi?

295
00:17:55,680 --> 00:17:57,200
I'd love nothing more than
to see him hacked to pieces!

296
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:57,720
No matter how useless he is,

297
00:17:57,720 --> 00:18:00,650
he's still the son
of both the Murong and Li families!

298
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,750
They were both switched at birth
and raised away from their real families.

299
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,810
Li Boze is the son of both families—
I acknowledge that.

300
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,720
But Murong Qingyi?

301
00:18:08,720 --> 00:18:10,720
He's just an outcast from both families!

302
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:11,510
Cousin,

303
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:13,030
only you treat that trash

304
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:14,560
like some prized treasure.

305
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:17,350
Huo Minxian,

306
00:18:17,920 --> 00:18:20,160
Murong Qingyi and Li Boze
were switched at birth.

307
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:21,640
Li Boze was raised in both families' favor

308
00:18:21,640 --> 00:18:22,790
and has an incredibly noble status.

309
00:18:22,790 --> 00:18:24,240
And who do you think you are?

310
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:26,240
The castoff neither family wants,
Murong Qingyi—

311
00:18:26,240 --> 00:18:28,240
he's exactly the match you deserve.

312
00:18:28,550 --> 00:18:30,000
What you did today

313
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:32,590
is beneath even those in brothels!

314
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,440
I have someone I love!

315
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,100
What's there to be ashamed of?

316
00:18:36,240 --> 00:18:37,440
Good, all the better.

317
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:40,400
I'll never marry my father's killer!

318
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,480
Huo Minxian!

319
00:18:42,160 --> 00:18:43,760
Take a good look at yourself!

320
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:45,790
I'm marrying you off

321
00:18:45,790 --> 00:18:47,440
just to secure the arms deal
between our two families—

322
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,970
a mere token of allegiance.

323
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:51,880
Do you really think
you're the family's prized daughter?

324
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:54,810
Even if I married you off to a dog
of the Murong family,

325
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:57,220
you'd still have to marry it obediently.

326
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,970
Your father died young.

327
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:06,680
If you and your mother

328
00:19:07,030 --> 00:19:08,630
wish to remain in the family,

329
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:10,590
you'd better be of use to it.

330
00:19:16,030 --> 00:19:16,830
Lock her up.

331
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:17,960
Go.

332
00:19:18,830 --> 00:19:20,270
Just say she couldn't bear the humiliation

333
00:19:20,270 --> 00:19:21,200
and took poison,

334
00:19:21,720 --> 00:19:24,240
and that she's currently receiving
emergency treatment at the hospital.

335
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:24,960
Let go of me!

336
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:26,720
I can walk by myself.

337
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:30,240
Young Master,

338
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:31,920
are you going to...

339
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:33,120
To the Murong family!

340
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,640
To demand an explanation from them.

341
00:19:38,660 --> 00:19:40,800
[Murong Residence]

342
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,350
My Lady, dinner is ready!

343
00:19:44,920 --> 00:19:46,050
Clear them all away.

344
00:19:47,830 --> 00:19:50,050
[Murong Jinrui,
Eldest Daughter of the Murong Family]

345
00:19:48,640 --> 00:19:49,510
My Lady,

346
00:19:49,790 --> 00:19:50,880
why did you decide

347
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:52,830
not to eat all these delicacies?

348
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,200
Delicacies, my foot.

349
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:56,920
This is swallows' spit mixed with blood.

350
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:58,580
These are scraps of shark fin.

351
00:19:58,640 --> 00:20:00,350
You call them delicacies?

352
00:20:00,510 --> 00:20:02,170
Even dogs wouldn't eat these.

353
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:03,880
Take them away.

354
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:05,310
Hurry up!

355
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:10,070
Now this is more like it.

356
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:13,680
So what?

357
00:20:14,310 --> 00:20:15,590
Mother dotes on me.

358
00:20:15,750 --> 00:20:17,480
I eat what I want

359
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:19,830
and say what I want.

360
00:20:20,270 --> 00:20:21,720
Who dares to have a problem with it?

361
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,830
My Lady, that's not what I meant.

362
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:26,160
I know.

363
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:28,350
Back then,

364
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:31,350
Mother followed Father on campaigns
all over the place

365
00:20:31,350 --> 00:20:33,350
and left me all alone in the countryside.

366
00:20:33,350 --> 00:20:35,240
She's trying to make it up to me.

367
00:20:35,480 --> 00:20:36,480
I understand.

368
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:39,640
But I grew up in the Northeast.

369
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:41,310
I genuinely can't stomach
that kind of food.

370
00:20:41,310 --> 00:20:43,240
Madam, Young Master, you're back.

371
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:45,720
My Lady,

372
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,590
Madam and the Young Masters
seem to have returned.

373
00:20:47,590 --> 00:20:48,240
What?

374
00:20:48,790 --> 00:20:51,240
That worthless Murong Qingyi is back too?

375
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:55,640
I heard he made quite a scene today.

376
00:20:56,350 --> 00:20:59,350
My Lady, we shouldn't
air our dirty laundry in public.

377
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:00,110
Take it.

378
00:21:00,640 --> 00:21:03,440
He can hardly be considered
a member of the family.

379
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,400
Are you okay, My Lady?

380
00:21:06,440 --> 00:21:07,590
Where are you going?

381
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:09,830
To catch the drama of the century!

382
00:21:18,510 --> 00:21:20,960
So the Huo girl really does have a lover?

383
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:23,880
Stop talking nonsense.

384
00:21:24,590 --> 00:21:26,190
Act like a proper young lady.

385
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,790
So, it's actually true?

386
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:30,790
So impetuous.

387
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:33,280
Sit here and speak properly.

388
00:21:36,750 --> 00:21:39,350
If the Huo family breaks off
the engagement,

389
00:21:39,720 --> 00:21:42,030
they probably won't sell that batch

390
00:21:42,400 --> 00:21:44,440
of highly sought-after arms to us.

391
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:48,880
Murong Qingyi has caused such a huge mess.

392
00:21:49,200 --> 00:21:51,270
He needs a proper lesson.

393
00:21:53,270 --> 00:21:54,000
Qingyu,

394
00:21:54,750 --> 00:21:56,110
as the eldest brother,

395
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:58,750
you should be the one
to deal with him first.

396
00:21:58,750 --> 00:21:59,350
Right?

397
00:22:03,270 --> 00:22:05,730
I'm afraid
he doesn't have the heart to do it.

398
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:13,870
Qingyi was switched at birth

399
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:15,690
and raised in the Li family.

400
00:22:16,070 --> 00:22:17,330
Naturally, bonds need

401
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,720
to be cultivated slowly

402
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,920
and rebuilt.

403
00:22:20,160 --> 00:22:21,960
But unfortunately, 3 years ago,

404
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:24,000
because of the Huo family incident,

405
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:25,480
he was thrown into prison.

406
00:22:26,110 --> 00:22:26,880
Now,

407
00:22:26,880 --> 00:22:28,590
without regard for his wishes,

408
00:22:28,590 --> 00:22:31,250
we're forcing him into this marriage
with a Huo.

409
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,920
It's understandable
that he has grievances.

410
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:35,180
He even has the nerve to have grievances?

411
00:22:38,510 --> 00:22:39,830
If he hadn't bungled

412
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:42,480
the delivery
of even a simple message back then,

413
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:44,540
would your father have died so young?

414
00:22:46,110 --> 00:22:46,880
Your father

415
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,460
once dominated the world.

416
00:22:48,480 --> 00:22:49,340
If he had to die,

417
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:50,960
it should've been on the battlefield—

418
00:22:50,960 --> 00:22:52,490
a soldier's death in glory!

419
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:54,830
My husband

420
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:58,440
deserved more than
such a plain, unremarkable death!

421
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:04,920
Mother,

422
00:23:05,550 --> 00:23:06,480
you know.

423
00:23:07,510 --> 00:23:09,110
Whether it's Father's death

424
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:10,640
or the Huo family incident,

425
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:13,020
there's something fishy about both.

426
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:14,920
Qingyi has been acting like that

427
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:15,980
simply because...

428
00:23:16,400 --> 00:23:17,720
he feels wronged.

429
00:23:22,030 --> 00:23:23,000
If you

430
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:25,200
could be a bit more patient with him...

431
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,730
Don't say I didn't warn you.

432
00:23:27,070 --> 00:23:29,240
You've been getting far too close to him—

433
00:23:29,240 --> 00:23:30,970
you might be letting danger in.

434
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:36,310
As Huo Minxian's lover,

435
00:23:36,310 --> 00:23:37,790
you actually did something like that.

436
00:23:37,790 --> 00:23:39,390
You're quite cold-blooded.

437
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:40,790
Lover?

438
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,880
I've been planning this for so long.

439
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,660
If you hadn't interfered,

440
00:23:48,110 --> 00:23:50,680
that vicious woman's scandal would've
spread across the whole city by now.

441
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:53,200
She would've already
killed herself in shame

442
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:54,660
and gone straight to hell.

443
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:58,330
You have a younger brother named Qin Xue.

444
00:23:58,400 --> 00:24:00,160
Last year, Huo Minxian drove him

445
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,490
to jump from a building.

446
00:24:02,030 --> 00:24:04,360
He's been on leave from school ever since.

447
00:24:04,680 --> 00:24:05,720
Am I right?

448
00:24:06,110 --> 00:24:07,440
Leave my brother alone.

449
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:08,970
That bitch deserves to die!

450
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:14,200
I don't care
what grudge you have against Huo Minxian,

451
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,830
but publicly screening something like that

452
00:24:16,830 --> 00:24:17,960
is too disgraceful.

453
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:19,400
Tell me,

454
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:21,360
where is the film negative?

455
00:24:30,920 --> 00:24:31,880
Not talking?

456
00:24:32,790 --> 00:24:34,790
Then you'd better think it through.

457
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:37,200
What will happen to your brother

458
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,350
if you die here?

459
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:56,790
Tell me.

460
00:25:01,680 --> 00:25:03,680
I was only responsible for the swap.

461
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,360
I don't know anything else.

462
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:08,200
I don't know where the negative is.

463
00:25:10,400 --> 00:25:12,590
Madam, Young Master Qingyu, Miss Jinrui,

464
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:15,450
people from the Huo family
have forced their way in.

465
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:22,110
Minxian couldn't bear it

466
00:25:22,110 --> 00:25:23,070
and took poison.

467
00:25:23,240 --> 00:25:25,110
She's hovering between life and death
in the hospital!

468
00:25:25,110 --> 00:25:27,270
You must give us an explanation!

469
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:29,700
What are you shouting for?

470
00:25:30,920 --> 00:25:32,520
With a scandal like today's,

471
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:34,240
it's your Huo family

472
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,720
that owes us an explanation.

473
00:25:35,720 --> 00:25:37,750
The suicide note says very clearly

474
00:25:37,920 --> 00:25:39,750
that the whole thing was fabricated.

475
00:25:39,750 --> 00:25:41,960
Minxian doesn't even know that rogue.

476
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:44,390
I've had people look into it.

477
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:46,030
The projectionist was knocked unconscious.

478
00:25:46,030 --> 00:25:48,400
That was your people's doing, wasn't it?

479
00:25:50,400 --> 00:25:51,160
Who did it?

480
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:52,590
Come out!

481
00:26:08,310 --> 00:26:09,200
Clean that up.

482
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,480
Young Master Huo.

483
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:21,070
What happened today

484
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,850
benefits neither of our families.

485
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:26,210
The Murong family has no reason

486
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,010
to sling mud at your family.

487
00:26:28,550 --> 00:26:29,350
Reason?

488
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:34,720
Isn't it all just to
make our family feel in the wrong

489
00:26:34,720 --> 00:26:36,550
so we'll bow our heads in shame

490
00:26:36,550 --> 00:26:38,480
and serve your family like slaves?

491
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,270
Listen up.

492
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:43,030
If anything happens to Minxian,

493
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:45,720
I won't let any of you off.

494
00:26:54,790 --> 00:26:55,880
Young Master Huo,

495
00:26:56,750 --> 00:26:58,550
everything requires evidence.

496
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,350
In this matter,

497
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:04,160
our family is the victim.

498
00:27:07,550 --> 00:27:08,440
Fine.

499
00:27:09,350 --> 00:27:10,350
Fine!

500
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,480
In that case,

501
00:27:13,790 --> 00:27:15,350
the engagement is off!

502
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:18,270
As for that batch of arms...

503
00:27:19,880 --> 00:27:21,750
Your Cheng Army
and the Li family's Ying Army

504
00:27:21,750 --> 00:27:24,410
are both fighting
for the North-South Railway.

505
00:27:24,590 --> 00:27:27,680
Just send your soldiers in
to fight with their bare hands.

506
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:28,920
I'm so scared.

507
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:32,070
No.

508
00:27:33,240 --> 00:27:35,570
The engagement must continue as planned.

509
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:37,680
Murong Qingyi and Miss Huo

510
00:27:37,790 --> 00:27:40,120
can publish a statement in the newspapers

511
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:42,000
clarifying that the film was fake

512
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,600
and that someone framed her.

513
00:27:45,880 --> 00:27:46,790
Miss Huo

514
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:50,010
has always been
a woman of impeccable virtue.

515
00:27:50,830 --> 00:27:51,550
Mother,

516
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,240
I think

517
00:27:53,440 --> 00:27:54,680
we should first hear Qingyi's opinion.

518
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:55,810
That's more like it!

519
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:01,060
You really are the lady of this house.

520
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,790
Why jeopardize our relations

521
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:03,880
over an outcast?

522
00:28:04,270 --> 00:28:05,830
That's hardly worth it, right?

523
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:07,160
However, Madam Murong,

524
00:28:07,240 --> 00:28:09,000
out of respect for our future kinship,

525
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:10,310
I've always given your family

526
00:28:10,310 --> 00:28:12,400
a discounted price on arms purchases.

527
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:14,260
Now, I'd like to raise it a little.

528
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:16,480
Thirty percent.

529
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:27,200
Don't push your luck.

530
00:28:27,750 --> 00:28:29,410
If you feel you're losing out,

531
00:28:29,590 --> 00:28:31,590
I can always do business elsewhere.

532
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:35,650
Young Master Qingyi, you're back.

533
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,890
Young Master Huo, you're here.

534
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,200
Open the chest.

535
00:28:48,510 --> 00:28:50,040
What are you going to do now?

536
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,000
All the negatives

537
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:56,480
the reporters took at the theater today

538
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,200
are here.

539
00:28:57,960 --> 00:29:00,820
And the newspapers
have all been bought off as well.

540
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:02,680
Young Master Huo,

541
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:04,070
how about we

542
00:29:04,200 --> 00:29:05,110
let today's matter end here?

543
00:29:05,110 --> 00:29:05,970
What do you say?

544
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:22,200
And if I refuse?

545
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:27,400
Arms—

546
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:29,830
if not from the Huo family,
there are other suppliers.

547
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:30,720
Worst case,

548
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:33,690
the Murong family
can simply back a new supplier.

549
00:29:34,830 --> 00:29:36,960
We're not dependent on your arms.

550
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:39,510
The Murong family sure talks tough.

551
00:29:40,000 --> 00:29:40,600
Very well.

552
00:29:41,680 --> 00:29:43,610
As it happens, I've been meaning to

553
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,720
pay a visit to Marshal Li Rongzhang.

554
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,440
I presume he'd be quite interested

555
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:49,040
in the arms business as well.

556
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:50,880
Laiyi,

557
00:29:51,550 --> 00:29:54,480
accompany Young Master Huo
to pay Marshal Li a visit.

558
00:29:55,030 --> 00:29:56,030
Tell him

559
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,680
that during the siege of Yingzhou,

560
00:29:57,680 --> 00:29:59,720
he lost hundreds of soldiers,

561
00:30:00,270 --> 00:30:02,960
all because the Huo family
hoarded supplies for profit

562
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:04,680
and delayed
the transport of military provisions.

563
00:30:04,680 --> 00:30:05,640
Bullshit!

564
00:30:06,790 --> 00:30:07,920
The evidence and witnesses

565
00:30:07,920 --> 00:30:10,270
are already in Marshal Li's office.

566
00:30:11,350 --> 00:30:12,310
Young Master Huo,

567
00:30:12,310 --> 00:30:14,170
why don't you go see for yourself?

568
00:30:17,550 --> 00:30:18,150
Oh, right.

569
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:21,530
Huo Minxian's lover is
in my hands as well.

570
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,830
If he

571
00:30:24,110 --> 00:30:26,310
starts talking nonsense to reporters,

572
00:30:26,350 --> 00:30:28,150
that wouldn't look good, right?

573
00:30:29,310 --> 00:30:30,750
I knew it was you.

574
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:33,880
Does it still matter

575
00:30:34,110 --> 00:30:35,110
whether it was me?

576
00:30:39,590 --> 00:30:41,750
We can let Miss Huo's scandal go.

577
00:30:42,550 --> 00:30:43,750
But that batch of arms

578
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:46,160
must be sold to us at the original price.

579
00:30:49,830 --> 00:30:50,400
Fine.

580
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:52,610
The wedding goes on,

581
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:53,400
and the price stays the same.

582
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,070
Not enough.

583
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:57,240
Brother,

584
00:30:57,830 --> 00:30:59,560
I'm the one being sold, not you.

585
00:31:01,030 --> 00:31:02,560
Am I really worth so little?

586
00:31:08,510 --> 00:31:09,640
I heard your family

587
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,970
recently imported several new aircraft.

588
00:31:12,070 --> 00:31:15,160
Young Master Huo, since you value
this marriage alliance so much,

589
00:31:15,160 --> 00:31:16,790
why not give them to Minxian
as part of her dowry?

590
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:17,240
What do you say?

591
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:18,110
Murong Qingyi!

592
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:20,270
Two versions of tomorrow's headline
have already

593
00:31:20,270 --> 00:31:23,160
been printed and are ready to
roll out across all of Nancheng.

594
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:24,590
Tomorrow's sensation—

595
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:27,920
whether it's
"Miss Huo Can't Forget Her Former Lover"

596
00:31:27,920 --> 00:31:30,960
or "Joyous Engagement
Between the Murong and Huo Families"—

597
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,160
is entirely up to you.

598
00:31:32,160 --> 00:31:33,360
Don't push your luck.

599
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:37,000
You can always refuse.

600
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:54,080
You'd better make sure nothing goes wrong.

601
00:31:55,550 --> 00:31:57,790
With several new aircraft as a dowry,

602
00:31:57,790 --> 00:31:59,450
how could I make any mistakes?

603
00:32:00,310 --> 00:32:01,310
Besides,

604
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:04,030
making the poisoned Miss Huo

605
00:32:04,200 --> 00:32:05,790
crawl out of her grave

606
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:07,800
isn't exactly a difficult task.

607
00:32:18,310 --> 00:32:19,270
It was you?

608
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:23,150
You were the one
who exposed Huo Minxian's affair?

609
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,830
You actually went
and made it public yourself?

610
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,250
Have you lost your mind?

611
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:33,590
Any normal man
in your position would've already

612
00:32:33,590 --> 00:32:35,350
bashed his head
against a wall out of shame.

613
00:32:35,350 --> 00:32:36,640
But look at you—

614
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:38,640
you don't feel the slightest shame,

615
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:40,440
yet you're gloating.

616
00:32:40,880 --> 00:32:41,480
You...

617
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:43,440
Look at you, acting like such an idiot.

618
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,510
Are you trying to
drive Mother and me to an early grave?

619
00:32:45,510 --> 00:32:47,200
So what if it was me?

620
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:49,200
I'm happy

621
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,260
that you're angry.

622
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:51,480
Is that a problem?

623
00:32:52,480 --> 00:32:53,030
Oh,

624
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:54,960
ease up on the anger,

625
00:32:55,440 --> 00:32:56,970
or you might just keel over.

626
00:32:57,750 --> 00:32:58,000
You...

627
00:32:58,000 --> 00:32:58,590
Enough.

628
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:01,760
Act like a proper young lady now.

629
00:33:11,350 --> 00:33:11,960
Qingyi!

630
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:20,750
You clearly didn't do that.

631
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:22,460
Why take the blame?

632
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:36,240
If you want to lecture me, Brother,

633
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,480
save your breath.

634
00:33:40,590 --> 00:33:41,310
Fine.

635
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:44,590
I never agreed to this marriage
to begin with.

636
00:33:44,590 --> 00:33:45,310
If you don't want it...

637
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:46,640
Who said I don't?

638
00:33:48,200 --> 00:33:50,130
I can't marry the one I love anyway,

639
00:33:50,200 --> 00:33:52,000
so it doesn't matter who I marry.

640
00:33:52,720 --> 00:33:55,200
Whether it's Huo Minxian or Chen Minxian,

641
00:33:55,790 --> 00:33:56,440
as long as

642
00:33:57,240 --> 00:33:58,790
I get what I want, it's fine.

643
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:03,510
You don't need to pity me.

644
00:34:04,720 --> 00:34:05,880
For now, I don't need

645
00:34:06,070 --> 00:34:07,590
you to be my savior.

646
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,150
The engagement banquet is tomorrow.

647
00:34:16,150 --> 00:34:17,480
Stay home tonight.

648
00:34:19,070 --> 00:34:22,110
And come with me to the pier
to pick up your sister-in-law.

649
00:34:22,110 --> 00:34:23,440
You haven't met her yet.

650
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:25,960
Home?

651
00:34:27,590 --> 00:34:28,719
Is this a home for me?

652
00:35:04,190 --> 00:35:05,000
Young Master Qingyi,

653
00:35:05,000 --> 00:35:06,070
I've looked into it.

654
00:35:06,070 --> 00:35:08,110
The one who screened the film
was Huo Minxian's lover.

655
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,230
But the one who took the negative

656
00:35:09,230 --> 00:35:11,160
appears to have been a young woman.

657
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,480
That woman must have

658
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:18,230
taken advantage of
the chaos in the theater,

659
00:35:18,230 --> 00:35:19,280
knocked out the projectionist,

660
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,610
and taken the negative.

661
00:35:22,030 --> 00:35:23,000
What's going on?

662
00:35:23,190 --> 00:35:25,190
Stop the screening! Stop it now!

663
00:35:25,480 --> 00:35:27,110
I said, stop the screening!

664
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:31,740
Stop taking pictures!

665
00:35:32,550 --> 00:35:33,440
Stop filming!

666
00:35:33,440 --> 00:35:35,440
Stop the screening! Stop it now!

667
00:35:35,800 --> 00:35:37,660
All of you, stop taking pictures!

668
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:39,410
Stop the screening!

669
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:41,540
-All of you, stop taking pictures!
-She only left that gentian flower.

670
00:35:41,540 --> 00:35:43,280
-Which newspaper are you from?
-But as for who she is...

671
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:43,920
Stop taking pictures!

672
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:44,690
Or where she went...

673
00:35:44,690 --> 00:35:45,640
Murong Qingyi!

674
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:47,930
-We have no clue.
-You're so despicable!

675
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:50,530
Should we keep investigating?

676
00:35:50,920 --> 00:35:51,760
Yes.

677
00:35:52,880 --> 00:35:53,880
Anyone bold enough to stir up trouble

678
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:56,320
right under the noses
of the Murong and Huo families

679
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:57,920
must be plotting something.

680
00:35:58,230 --> 00:35:58,960
Understood.

681
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:01,360
The engagement banquet is tomorrow.

682
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:04,220
Young Master Qingyi,
please retire early tonight.

683
00:36:13,630 --> 00:36:15,150
Welcome, distinguished guests,

684
00:36:15,150 --> 00:36:16,590
to the engagement celebration

685
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:18,110
of the Murong family's Eldest Young Master

686
00:36:18,110 --> 00:36:20,630
and Miss Fang of Nanyang,
as well as the Murong family's

687
00:36:20,630 --> 00:36:21,920
Second Young Master
and Miss Huo of Nancheng.

688
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:24,480
Please welcome Miss Huo Minxian!

689
00:36:41,880 --> 00:36:42,590
Next,

690
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:44,960
please welcome Miss Fang Mulan.

691
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,020
♪ Take away everything I have ♪

692
00:36:50,050 --> 00:36:51,960
♪ Can you bear the weight of it all? ♪

693
00:36:53,050 --> 00:36:54,750
♪ I offer you my whole life ♪

694
00:36:54,820 --> 00:36:56,390
♪ In exchange for everything you have ♪

695
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:58,500
♪ Can I claim it as mine? ♪

696
00:36:59,550 --> 00:37:01,360
♪ Give me love and hate ♪

697
00:37:01,490 --> 00:37:04,900
♪ Let the tears fall,
let the blood spill ♪

698
00:37:05,020 --> 00:37:07,720
♪ Even through suffering,
I'll never let go of your hand ♪

699
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:08,070
Three years...

700
00:37:08,600 --> 00:37:11,360
♪ I can't break free, I can't escape ♪

701
00:37:09,590 --> 00:37:10,360
A dead woman

702
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:11,960
is standing before me once again.

703
00:37:11,390 --> 00:37:13,870
♪ This, too, can be called
a lifetime together ♪

704
00:37:13,800 --> 00:37:15,070
She's alive,

705
00:37:13,950 --> 00:37:15,150
♪ We ♪

706
00:37:16,110 --> 00:37:17,280
but I've gone mad.

707
00:37:16,600 --> 00:37:18,200
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

708
00:37:19,530 --> 00:37:23,650
♪ Forevermore ♪
